reviewText: I JUST LOVE TO HEAR R. KELLY SING AND DO HIS THING. THE MUSIC IS SWEET AND HE LOOKS HANDSOME AS EVER. YOU ALL JUST HAVE TO GET THIS. IT IS SOME FEEL GOOD MUSIC. R.
